column5: Hey everybody, I'm the new guy here, I love to fish for all species but float fishing with a centerpin has been my passion for the last couple of years but I hope to learn a lot from some of you and maybe teach a little.
welcome, I also just joined today. definitely a lot to learn in this forum from what I've read so far, welcome!!!!!
Welcome aboard PDG. There are lots of float reel nuts here too....but if variety is your thing as well....were like a box of chocolates....you never know what you get..lol
Welcome PDG. Make yourself at home.
Welcome to OFC.    OK - I have to ask ... what does PDG stand for.
Welcome to OFC.    OK - I have to ask ... what does PDG stand for.  "Pretty Dang Good"   LOL
Glad you stopped in and welcome to the forum.   Art
